[node name="THE TOOLS" type="RichTextLabel" parent="Center/MainPanel/VBox/TabContainer"]
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0.101961, 0.101961, 0.101961, 1)
theme_override_constants/line_separation = 6
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b][color=#000000]SIEM LOG VIEWER[/color][/b]
The source of forensic truth. Locate events that match your investigation. [color=#666666]DRAG[/color] logs onto tickets to build a case.

[b][color=#000000]EMAIL ANALYZER[/color][/b]
Where threats are first identified. Don't just read—analyze. Use [i]Check Links[/i] and [i]View Headers[/i] to find hidden IPs and hostnames.

[b][color=#000000]TERMINAL[/color][/b]
Your active defense system. 
- [code]scan [hostname][/code]: Verify if a host is actually infected.
- [code]isolate [hostname][/code]: Disconnect a threat from the network immediately.

[b][color=#000000]NETWORK MAP[/color][/b]
Real-time topology. Monitor host statuses (Clean, Suspicious, Infected, Isolated) to maintain situational awareness."
metadata/_tab_index = 0

[node name="THE RULES" type="RichTextLabel" parent="Center/MainPanel/VBox/TabContainer"]
visible = false
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0.101961, 0.101961, 0.101961, 1)
theme_override_constants/line_separation = 6
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b][color=#2E7D32]COMPLIANT RESOLUTION[/color][/b]
Slow but perfect. Requires all evidence. [color=#2E7D32]+ Integrity Bonus.[/color]

[b][color=#F57C00]EFFICIENT RESOLUTION[/color][/b]
Fast but risky. Resolves the ticket quickly but may miss hidden threats. No integrity bonus.

[b][color=#C62828]EMERGENCY PROTOCOL[/color][/b]
Instant containment. Forces the ticket closed immediately. Use only when the network is collapsing. [color=#C62828]Large Integrity Penalty.[/color]

[b][color=#006CFF]PROCEDURAL VIOLATIONS[/color][/b]
Executing high-risk commands (like Isolate) without forensic justification (Scan) will damage organization stability and trigger internal audits."
metadata/_tab_index = 1

[node name="THE KILL CHAIN" type="RichTextLabel" parent="Center/MainPanel/VBox/TabContainer"]
visible = false
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0.101961, 0.101961, 0.101961, 1)
theme_override_constants/line_separation = 6
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "[b]THREAT EVOLUTION[/b]
If a ticket is ignored or resolved incorrectly, the threat matures.

[b]Stage 1: INFILTRATION[/b] - Initial access. Low impact.
[b]Stage 2: PROPAGATION[/b] - Malware spreads to other hosts.
[b]Stage 3: EXFILTRATION[/b] - Critical data loss. Huge integrity hit.
[b]Stage 4: IMPACT[/b] - Systems go offline. Termination imminent.

[b][color=#F57C00]BLACK TICKETS[/color][/b]
Rare, high-stakes recovery assignments that offer a final chance to prevent organization bankruptcy after major breaches."
metadata/_tab_index = 2

